pkgmetadata.longdescription: # honeycomb-stubs[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/honeycomb-stubs)](https://pypi.org/project/honeycomb-stubs/)Python type stubs for: * [libhoney](https://github.com/honeycombio/libhoney-py) * [beeline](https://github.com/honeycombio/beeline-python)The stubs for `beeline` are relatively complete, but the stubs for `libhoney`are woefully incomplete. PRs welcome!## Usage```pip install honeycomb-stubs```
